<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589722>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pseudolaryngodus spectabilis gen. et sp. nov. a, HOLOTYPE male, habitus, dorsal view; b, same, ventral view; c, PARATYPE male, abdominal dorsum; d, same, abdominal venter. Abbreviations: sgs, scent gland scars; sp, spiracles; tb, trichobothria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589722/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589724>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pseudolaryngodus spectabilis gen. et sp. nov. PARATYPE male. a, pygophore, posterodorsal view; b–e, left paramere, four different aspects; f, aedeagus, lateral view; g, same, dorsal view. Abbreviations: b, body; ba, basal apparatus; c, conjunctiva; dl, dorsal lobe; gp, gonoporal process; hp, helicoid process; hs, holding sclerite; ll, lateral lobe; ml, membranous lobe; n, neck; p, phallotheca; vl, ventral lobe; w, wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589724/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589727>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Laryngodus luteomaculatus, male. a, habitus, dorsal view; b, abdominal dorsum; c, abdominal venter. Abbreviations: ilt, inner laterotergite; sp, spiracles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2589729>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Laryngodus luteomaculatus, male. a, pygophore, posterodorsal view; b, aedeagus, dorsal view; c–f, left paramere, four different aspects." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2589729/files/figure.png" ;
